---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Note — AmirHossein Movahedi", seo={{
	title: "Note AmirHossein Movahedi",
	description: "Learn about my background, interests in complex systems and neuroscience."
	}}>
	<main class="page">
		<section class="card">
			<div class="card-header">
      <h2>📝 Notes & downloads</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="card-content">
        <p>In this part you can see the Note that I want to share, also you can 
          download it.</p>		
		  		
        <div class="interest-item">
          <h2>📄 The problem that solve in selected topic course</h2>
          <p>
            <!-- <a href="/linearalg.pdf" class="download-link" target="_blank">Download the PDF (resume / notes)</a> -->
            <li><a href="/public/statistical/HW1/Hw1.pdf" class="download-link">1</a></li>
            <p><small>PDF, 41 KB</small></p>
           </p>			
		    <p>
            <!-- <a href="/linearalg.pdf" class="download-link" target="_blank">Download the PDF (resume / notes)</a> -->
            <li><a href="public/statistical/HW2/report.md" class="download-link">2</a></li>
            <p><small>markdown, 12 KB</small></p>
           </p>		
		    <p>
            <!-- <a href="/linearalg.pdf" class="download-link" target="_blank">Download the PDF (resume / notes)</a> -->
            <li><a href="public/statistical/HW1/Hw3.pdf" class="download-link">3</a></li>
            <p><small>PDF, 53 KB</small></p>
           </p>		
		</div>
			<br>
			<div class="interest-item">
          <h2>Comming soon !!</h2>	
		</div>



			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page {
	padding: 60px 6vw 120px;
	display: grid;
	gap: 60px;
}
.card {
		background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		padding: 48px;
		border-radius: 24px;
		backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
		transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, border 0.25s ease;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-8px);
		border: 1px solid  rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.3);;
		box-shadow:
			0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35),
			0 0 30px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.15);
	}
	.card-header {
		margin-bottom: 32px;
		padding-bottom: 16px;
		border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
	}

	.card h2 {
		font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
		font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 1.9rem);
		margin: 0;
		color:  #ffffff;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.card-content {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
	}
	.card-content p {
		margin: 0 0 20px;
	}

	.card-content p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.interests-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(600px, 1fr));
		gap: 24px;
	}

	.interest-item {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11, 229, 245, 0.08), rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08));
		border: 1px solid rgba(11, 124, 245, 0.2);
		padding: 24px;
		border-radius: 16px;
		transition: all 0.25s ease;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.interest-item h3 {
		font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin: 0 0 12px;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.interest-item p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		margin: 0;
	}

  .download-link {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: wheat;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .download-link:hover {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>

